DescDetail: <<
oRTP is a LGPL licensed C library implementing the RTP protocol (rfc3550).

Current features:
* works with ipv6
* packet scheduler
* adaptive jitter compensation
* automatic sending of RTCP SR or RR coumpounded with a SDES
* RTCP parser API
<<

